text: Yunus Emre Sonsırma (born October 8, 1992) is a Turkish professional basketball player for Pınar Karşıyaka of the Turkish Basketball Super League. ==Turkish national team== He played for the Turkey U-20 National Team. ==External links== * TBL Profile Category:1992 births Category:Büyükçekmece Basketbol players Category:Eskişehir Basket players Category:Living people Category:Darüşşafaka SK players Category:Karşıyaka basketball players Category:Point guards Category:Turkish men's basketball players Category:Türk Telekom B.K. players
